{
  "stem": "12674.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because unless I can buy myself something that I want for that money, I don't need to make it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "By that time, the children were going-- you know, it was getting later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The children were going to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I wasn't as-- as-- and I was making more money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I developed a bigger mouth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was more sure of myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyway, I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I have been going religiously back ever since, every single year, until I picked up with Hyman.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "After the first three, four years, he said he wants to see the world.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We went to other places.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we made a bargain, every other year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So every other year, I go for six, seven weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in between, if there is a-- a wedding or something, I go the year that we go someplace else, I take another couple of weeks extra and I go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I feel--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What it means is number one, when I came out of the war, I found that many people had had far worse-- what I considered worse-- experience than my own.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I always-- I think what happened to me is a nightmare.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's worse than a nightmare.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's-- it's something that's unimaginable among sane people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when I heard some of the stories that other people talked about, gas chambers and mountains of people, and mountains of hair, and-- I felt like I wasn't tattooed.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I felt like I didn't qualify to be-- to consider myself a member of the-- of the club.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I felt all the years, I have to pay a price.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why was I chosen?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What did I?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't even pray to God.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why was I chosen?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why-- why-- why was I survive?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I felt I owed all the people.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
